<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Abraham's Blog</title><link>https://blog.inshomepgup.com/</link><description/><language>en-us</language><lastBuildDate>Fri, 14 Feb 2025 00:00:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://blog.inshomepgup.com/post/git/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>windows 安装 git 的推荐设置</title><link>https://blog.inshomepgup.com/p/windows-%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85-git-%E7%9A%84%E6%8E%A8%E8%8D%90%E8%AE%BE%E7%BD%AE/</link><pubDate>Sun, 16 Feb 2025 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://blog.inshomepgup.com/p/windows-%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85-git-%E7%9A%84%E6%8E%A8%E8%8D%90%E8%AE%BE%E7%BD%AE/</guid><description>&lt;p>我截图界面的就是推荐关闭或者打开的配置项目&lt;/p>
